  "title": "HEAVY TRUCK DRIVER",
  "description": "<p></p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p>1. Transport soil from one site to another site</p><p>2. Follow a schedule for deliveries of soil</p><p>3. Verify and understand the type of soil as well as weight, not to overload</p><p>4. Clear communication and co-ordination with other equipment operator at worksite</p><p>5. Handle, drive and control truck in a safe, considerate and professional manner</p><p>6. Keep truck in good working order<br /><br />7. Singapore Class 4 driving license must be more than 2 years</p><p></p>",
